typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		SalesOrderID as integer,
		RevisionNumber as byte,
		OrderDate as timestamp,
		DueDate as timestamp,
		ShipDate as timestamp,
		Status as byte,
		OnlineOrderFlag as boolean,
		SalesOrderNumber as string,
		PurchaseOrderNumber as string,
		AccountNumber as string,
		CustomerID as integer,
		ShipToAddressID as integer,
		BillToAddressID as integer,
		ShipMethod as string,
		CreditCardApprovalCode as string,
		SubTotal as decimal(19,4),
		TaxAmt as decimal(19,4),
		Freight as decimal(19,4),
		TotalDue as decimal(19,4),
		Comment as string,
		rowguid as string,
		ModifiedDate as timestamp
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> source1
source1 derive(Year = year(OrderDate),
		Month = month(OrderDate)) ~> YearMonth
YearMonth aggregate(groupBy(CustomerID,
		Year,
		Month),
	TotalSales = sum(SubTotal),
		TotalTax = sum(TaxAmt),
		TotalDue = sum(TotalDue),
		TotalFreight = sum(Freight)) ~> AggrgateProfitLoss
AggrgateProfitLoss sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	deletable:false,
	insertable:true,
	updateable:false,
	upsertable:false,
	format: 'table',
	mapColumn(
		CustomerID,
		Year,
		Month,
		TotalSales,
		TotalTax,
		TotalDue,
		TotalFreight
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SlaesFact

source(output(
		Empid as string,
		Empname as string,
		Department as string,
		City as string,
		LastModifiedDate as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false) ~> EmpDataCsv
source(output(
		SID as integer,
		Empid as string,
		Empname as string,
		Department as string,
		City as string,
		LastModifiedDate as string,
		Indicator as integer
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> source1
source(output(
		max_key as integer
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select max([SID]) as max_key from [dbo].[EmpDimT2]',
	format: 'query') ~> Maxkey
source1 select(mapColumn(
		DimSID = SID,
		DimEmpid = Empid,
		DimEmpname = Empname,
		DimDepartment = Department,
		DimCity = City,
		DimLastModifiedDate = LastModifiedDate,
		DimIndicator = Indicator
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> Select1
EmpDataCsv, Maxkey join(1==1,
	joinType:'cross',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Join1
Join1, Select1 lookup(Empid == DimEmpid,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Lookup1
Lookup1 split(isNull(DimEmpid),
	disjoint: false) ~> ConditionalSplit1@(Insert, Exists)
ConditionalSplit1@Insert derive(Indicator = 1) ~> DerivedColumn1
DerivedColumn1 sink(input(
		SID as integer,
		Empid as string,
		Empname as string,
		Department as string,
		City as string,
		LastModifiedDate as string,
		Indicator as integer
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	deletable:false,
	insertable:true,
	updateable:false,
	upsertable:false,
	format: 'table',
	mapColumn(
		Empid,
		Empname,
		Department,
		City,
		LastModifiedDate,
		Indicator
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> sink1

source(output(
		Empid as string,
		Empname as string,
		Department as string,
		City as string,
		LastModifiedDate as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> source1
source1 alterRow(upsertIf(1==1)) ~> AlterRow1
AlterRow1 sink(input(
		Empid as string,
		Empname as string,
		Department as string,
		City as string,
		LastModifiedDate as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	deletable:false,
	insertable:false,
	updateable:false,
	upsertable:true,
	keys:['Empid'],
	format: 'table',
	mapColumn(
		Empid,
		Empname,
		Department,
		City,
		LastModifiedDate
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> sink1

source(output(
		CustomerID as string,
		CompanyName as string,
		ContactName as string,
		ContactTitle as string,
		Address as string,
		City as string,
		OrderID as integer,
		OrderDate as timestamp,
		Freight as decimal(19,4),
		ShipAddress as string,
		ShipCity as string,
		ShipCountry as string,
		ShipPostalCode as string,
		ShipRegion as string,
		ProductID as integer,
		Quantity as short,
		UnitPrice as decimal(19,4)
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'SELECT    Customers.CustomerID, Customers.CompanyName, Customers.ContactName, Customers.ContactTitle, Customers.Address, Customers.City, Orders.OrderID, Orders.OrderDate, Orders.Freight, Orders.ShipAddress,            Orders.ShipCity, Orders.ShipCountry, Orders.ShipPostalCode, Orders.ShipRegion, [Order Details].ProductID, [Order Details].Quantity, [Order Details].UnitPriceFROM      Customers INNER JOIN            Orders ON Customers.CustomerID = Orders.CustomerID INNER JOIN            [Order Details] ON Orders.OrderID = [Order Details].OrderID\n',
	format: 'query') ~> source1
source1 sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	deletable:false,
	insertable:true,
	updateable:false,
	upsertable:false,
	truncate:true,
	format: 'table',
	mapColumn(
		CustomerID,
		CompanyName,
		ContactName,
		ContactTitle,
		Address,
		City,
		OrderID,
		OrderDate,
		Freight,
		ShipAddress,
		ShipCity,
		ShipCountry,
		ShipPostalCode,
		ShipRegion,
		ProductID,
		Quantity,
		UnitPrice
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> sink1

source(output(
		SalesOrderID as integer,
		RevisionNumber as byte,
		OrderDate as timestamp,
		DueDate as timestamp,
		ShipDate as timestamp,
		Status as byte,
		OnlineOrderFlag as boolean,
		SalesOrderNumber as string,
		PurchaseOrderNumber as string,
		AccountNumber as string,
		CustomerID as integer,
		ShipToAddressID as integer,
		BillToAddressID as integer,
		ShipMethod as string,
		CreditCardApprovalCode as string,
		SubTotal as decimal(19,4),
		TaxAmt as decimal(19,4),
		Freight as decimal(19,4),
		TotalDue as decimal(19,4),
		Comment as string,
		rowguid as string,
		ModifiedDate as timestamp
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> SaleOrdHdr
source(output(
		SalesOrderID as integer,
		SalesOrderDetailID as integer,
		OrderQty as short,
		ProductID as integer,
		UnitPrice as decimal(19,4),
		UnitPriceDiscount as decimal(19,4),
		LineTotal as decimal(38,6),
		rowguid as string,
		ModifiedDate as timestamp
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> SaleOrdItem
source(output(
		ProductID as integer,
		Name as string,
		ProductNumber as string,
		Color as string,
		StandardCost as decimal(19,4),
		ListPrice as decimal(19,4),
		Size as string,
		Weight as decimal(8,2),
		ProductCategoryID as integer,
		ProductModelID as integer,
		SellStartDate as timestamp,
		SellEndDate as timestamp,
		DiscontinuedDate as timestamp,
		ThumbNailPhoto as binary,
		ThumbnailPhotoFileName as string,
		rowguid as string,
		ModifiedDate as timestamp
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table') ~> Product
SaleOrdHdr, SaleOrdItem join(SaleOrdHdr@SalesOrderID == SaleOrdItem@SalesOrderID,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> SaleHdrItemJoin
SaleHdrItemJoin select(mapColumn(
		SalesOrderNo = SaleOrdHdr@SalesOrderID,
		OrderDate,
		OrderFlag = OnlineOrderFlag,
		CustomerID,
		SubTotal,
		TaxAmt,
		Freight,
		TotalDue,
		OrderQty,
		ProductID,
		UnitPrice,
		UnitPriceDiscount,
		LineTotal
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> HdrItemselection
HdrItemselection, Product join(HdrItemselection@ProductID == Product@ProductID,
	joinType:'inner',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> ProductSaleDetailsJoin
ProductSaleDetailsJoin select(mapColumn(
		SalesOrderNo,
		OrderDate,
		OrderFlag,
		CustomerID,
		SubTotal,
		TaxAmt,
		Freight,
		TotalDue,
		OrderQty,
		ProductID = HdrItemselection@ProductID,
		UnitPrice,
		UnitPriceDiscount,
		LineTotal,
		StandardCost,
		ListPrice,
		ProductCategoryID,
		ProductModelID
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> Select1
Select1 sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	deletable:false,
	insertable:true,
	updateable:false,
	upsertable:false,
	format: 'table',
	mapColumn(
		SalesOrderNo,
		OrderDate,
		OrderFlag,
		CustomerID,
		SubTotal,
		TaxAmt,
		Freight,
		TotalDue,
		OrderQty,
		ProductID,
		UnitPrice,
		UnitPriceDiscount,
		LineTotal,
		StandardCost,
		ListPrice,
		ProductCategoryID,
		ProductModelID
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> sink1

source(output(
		sno as integer,
		{financial year} as integer,
		quarter as string,
		amount as integer
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	preferredIntegralType: 'integer') ~> ActualFile
ActualFile sink(input(
		sno as string,
		{financial year} as string,
		quarter as string,
		amount as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	partitionFileNames:['ActualData.csv'],
	mapColumn(
		{financial year},
		quarter,
		amount
	),
	partitionBy('hash', 1),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> sink1

	validateSchema: false,
	partitionFileNames:['SlaesFact.txt'],

	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> Sink1
